page.title: 20CREDITS
page.content:
We would like to thank the many local people,too numerous to mention,who have helped us in the completion of our work.The following children,under the supervision and editorial direction of Mr.D.Ireland and Mr.A.Hyde,were responsible for the text and the survey work.
P.Bunting,M.Cox,B.Cutting,R.Finney, D.Greetham,W.Hollingsworth,C.Maltby, R.Nolan,I.Peverett,J.Scarborough, D.Sharp,M.Widdop,S.Baxter,C.Curtis, M.Czajkowski,J.Draper,D.Jackson, T.Lannen,K.Lovatt,T.Mills,S.Ockleford, H.Picker,S.Wilkinson,S.Hutton,L.Gordon
We would also like to thank the library and other local institutions which have helped.
